name: Tompkins County Health Department
tweet: @BillsMafia835 NYS has delegated enforcement of the mandate to local Health Departments. TCHD is awaiting further resources & information from NYS. TCHD will communicate more details on the State mandate and enforcement efforts as they become available.

name: Tompkins County Health Department
tweet: “This disease is still impacting people in our community, we have seen ongoing hospitalizations & deaths from COVID-19. We’re asking that you wear a mask while around others indoors & get vaccinated – these are safe & effective ways to reduce the most harmful impacts of COVID19.”  https://t.co/FTJvruBiH9

name: Tompkins County Health Department
tweet: @TompkinsHealth is awaiting further resources & info. from NYS, as capacity is limited due to ongoing pandemic response activities incl. contact tracing, testing, & vaccination. We will communicate more details on the State mandate & enforcement efforts as they become available.
